Text: Epsilon wakes up early.

She sleeps for three hours. But thanks to a technique
she learned from her lord to magically remove fatigue
while asleep, those three hours are plenty.
Needless to say, it doesn't affect her looks either.

This sleep schedule allows her to make effective use
of the remaining 21 hours in the day.

Epsilon fills her days with training and missions,
of course, but she places utmost importance on
time devoted to self-improvement.

And that's why she stands in front of the mirror
early each morning.
Another day begins, and I am still...
Beautiful!!!

Her very first order of business is to check her
ample, slime-enhanced bust.

Is it big and shaped nicely? Is it perky and soft to
the touch? And most importantly of all, does it
look natural?

No one must be allowed to discover this most
voluptuous secret.

Her chest must be more natural than natural, more
real than real. With that policy in mind, Epsilon's
inspections of her slime leave no room for error.

Next, she checks the overall balance of her
proportions.

Is her slim hourglass silhouette, bound in place with
slime, satisfactory? Is the volume of her slime-
padded hips appealing to the eye?

Then there is the taper and plumpness of her thighs,
the shape of her calves, the length of her legs...

The morning sun is already up by the time she
finishes going over everything.
Perfect.

Everything up to this point is part of her daily
routine.

When I met my master, I gained the power to resist
two fates.
What is this...?
This is the power to change fate.

By altering your appearance at will, it is possible
to change even the fate of loss into victory.
Fate...

Alter your fate, and seize the truth hiding in the
shadows of the world.
The truth...
...will be mine!
My lord, I will show you that I can be victorious...
Naturally!!!
Beta's pen races intently across her manuscript.
The Chronicles of Master Shadow, Book 1, Chapter 2...

Red eyes that shine more brilliantly than the moon
above and wavy hair so glossy it puts even silk to
shame.

Words spin together with a black darkness so
beautiful and virile that even demons fall to
their knees.
I see it now.

You're the stray with the body honed to the golden
ratio and flawless features that's snapping at the
heels of the Cult.
He called Master Shadow a stray dog!
My name is Shadow.

I lurk in the darkness and hunt down shadows. And
I will guide that lovely elf over there to safety.
Master Shadow...!
Sorry to keep you waiting, my gorgeous elven maiden.
I will fly to you at once...
At once...
Ugh, itâ€™s no good!
This is just a little too dramatic.

As if I could make some cheap floozy like her into
the heroine!
Maybe I'll try stepping outside for some air.
Now where did I put my clothes...

After leaving their respective bedrooms, Beta and
Epsilon run into each other for the first time in
a while in the courtyard.
Good morning, Beta.
Good morning, Epsilon.

They exchange what on the surface appears to be
pleasant greetings.

Just a casual morning hello. However, their eyes
never once look at each other's face.
No, their eyes are only on each other's...chests.

The intensity of the gazes directed at each other's
rocket-like breasts is such that one would think
they are looking their parents' murderer in the
eye.
This is a battle no woman ever wants to lose.
Hehehe...
Grr...
Epsilon reigns supreme yet again today.

The reason being that she insures her slime always
amasses in a way that will outshine Beta.

This conflict originates with some one-sided
hostility from Epsilon.

However, as Epsilon continued with her enhancements,
the seeds of competitiveness naturally sprouted within
Beta, too, and now they both harbor pits of inky black
anger in their bosoms.
Maybe I'm just imagining things...

but I feel like our lord is paying me a lot of
attention lately.
I feel his hot gaze...right...here.

There is no way that's true! Your mind is playing
tricks on you!

It is not. You must know what I'm talking about,
right? After all, you and I are far more sensitive
to those kinds of looks than the others.
...You have a point.

But I just wonder if it's fair that me, little ol' me,
gets showered with such amorous glances
from our lord?

Oh, but I'm sure you must've had your share of steamy
looks from our lord, too, right? Your boobs do put my
own to shame, after all.
Oh dear, could it be you haven't?
Urk...
What are the two of you up to, just standing there?
Oh, Nu. Good morning.
Is something the matter?
*sigh*
I have orders from Lady Alpha.
